The final doorway in the Electric Castle. What lies beyond? Treasure beyond imagining, or doom? Only one way to learn the answer.

When you peer into the mirror, rather than a reflection, you can make out some other location through a swirling mist. 

When you reach out to touch it, your hand passes into the mirror. Perhaps you can walk through to the destination you see...
Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.

Very, very, dry herbs. How they've managed to survive the ages is a mystery. 

They still smell quite pleasant though.

((OOC note - these are to be used by those of EVIL Alignment ONLY. No exceptions.))
